http://www.cpac.org:80/empower/speech02.html 204.71.237.74 19970108104245 text/html 29941
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 10:43:00 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 02-Jul-96 21:03:48 GMT
