http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/spotlights/8-28-95/gramspee.html 204.71.237.74 19970122012650 text/html 16559
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 01:26:41 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Oct-95 14:26:36 GMT
Content-length: 16372
