<DOCNO>WT19-B27-64</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA087-000633-B032-131</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/heritage/jobs/sales.html 204.71.237.74 19970122024555 text/html 2297
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 02:46:15 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 17-Nov-95 16:30:14 GMT
