<DOCNO>WT19-B27-65</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA074-000493-B018-346</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/infotain/8-18-95/kickoff.html.cgi/textonly 204.71.237.74 19970122001153 text/html 9313
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
