http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/infotain/8-18-95/gingrich.html.cgi/textonly 204.71.237.74 19970122001241 text/html 1771
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 00:13:04 GMT
