<html>
<head>
<title>American Civilization - April 1995 -- PFF</title>
</head>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/pff/notebook.gif" LINK="#8C1717" VLINK="#545454" ALINK="#FF0000"> <ul><blockquote><a href="/pff"><img src="/pff/pffdoc.gif" align="right" border="0"></a>
<center>
<br>
<br>
<h2>American Civilization<br></h2>
<b>Volume 1, Issue 5 -- April 1995</b>
<hr width="55%">
</center>
<p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/pff/amciv/ac-april/ac495jb.html">The Myth of the Coming Balanced Budget Recession</a> ...by John E. Berthoud<br>
<li><a href="/pff/amciv/ac-april/ac495fs.html">Foresight: Religion, Politics, and Society An Interview with Ralph Reed</a><br>
<li><a href="/pff/amciv/ac-april/ac495gg.html">The Freedom Model of Telecommunications Deregulation</a> ...by George Gilder<br>
<li><a href="/pff/amciv/ac-april/ac495ng.html">If We Believe in the Declaration, We've Got to Transform our Culture</a> ...by Newt Gingrich<br>
<li><a href="/pff/amciv/ac-april/ac495ph.html">Civilized Reading:  <b>The Amercian Presidency: An Intellectual History</b></a> ...review by Phillip G. Henderson<br>
<li><a href="/pff/amciv/ac-april/ac495jj.html">America's Manufacturing Revolution:  The New Economy</a> ...by Jerry Jasinowski<br>
<li><a href="/pff/amciv/ac-april/ac495jk.html">Common Sense Welfare Reform Act</a> ...by Joe Knollenberg<br>
<li><a href="/pff/amciv/ac-april/ac495el.html">The American Idea and American Promise</a> ...by Everett Carll Ladd<br>
<li><a href="/pff/amciv/ac-april/ac495sl.html">Misunderstanding Microsoft</a> ...by Stan Lievowitz<br>
<li><a href="/pff/amciv/ac-april/ac495mr.html">Condemning the Successful</a> ...by Michael Rothschild<br>
<li><a href="/pff/amciv/ac-april/ac495js.html">A Nation of Cowards</a> ...by Jeffrey R. Snyder<br>
<li><a href="/pff/amciv/ac-april/ac495st.html">Statement of Principles on Telecommunications Policy</a>
<p>
<li><a href="/pff/amciv/ac-april/ac495ms.html">Credits</a>
</ul>
<br>
<center>
</center>
</p>
</blockquote></ul><p><br><center><a href="/pff/footer.map"><img src="/pff/footer.gif" border="0" ISMAP></a></center></BODY>
