http://www.cpac.org:80/ads/ve/debates.html 204.71.237.74 19970122022514 text/html 5307
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 02:25:32 GMT
