<DOCNO>WT19-B27-233</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA086-000618-B004-73</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/nmp/wr-7-95.html 204.71.237.74 19970121230110 text/html 12464
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 21-Jan-97 23:01:29 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Oct-95 14:26:00 GMT
Content-length: 12279
