http://www.cpac.org:80/nmp/pub-1295.html 204.71.237.74 19970109112250 text/html 3686
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 11:23:07 GMT
